import React from "react"

function AddPlantForm (){
   return (
    <form style={{display : 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', paddingRight : '30'}}>
        <label>
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Plant Name" style={{paddingRight: '60px'}} />
        </label>
        <label>
        <input type="url" name="url" placeholder="Image URL" style={{paddingRight: '50px'}}/>
        </label>
        <label>
        <input type="number" name="price" placeholder="Price" style={{paddingRight: '50px'}}/>
        </label>
        <button type="submit" style={{padding: '0 30px 0 30px', border: 'none'}}>Add Plant</button>
    </form>
    )

}
export default AddPlantForm
